import React from 'react'
import {
    Form,
    FormGroup,
    Label,
    Input,
    Button,
    Link
} from 'reactstrap';

export const AddUser = () => {
    return (
        <Form>
            <FormGroup>
                <Label>Name</Label>
                <Input
                  type="text"
                  name="name"
                  placeholder="Enter Name"
                    autocomplete="off"></Input>
            </FormGroup>
            <Button type="submit" className="btn">Submit</Button>
            <Link to="/" className="btn btn-danger ml-2">Cancel</Link>
        </Form>
    )
}
